 Charity, Unity, Fraternity, Patriotism - Knights of Columbus
WELCOME to our Knights of Columbus online store
The English Company Inc. is family owned and operated by KofC Knights. We have been an established and popular company in the Order with an excellent track record for best customer satisfaction. We have never compromised on the quality and the services provided to the customer. We believe in keeping the customers happy and providing them with products at a competent price. We also take tremendous pride in being the leading designated official supplier and manufacturer for the Knights of Columbus in the United States.
 Order online 24 hours a day or by phone 1-800-444-5632 9:00 am-5:00 pm EST, Monday-Friday  Pay with Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, Personal/Council/Assembly Checks and Money Orders. 
What some of our customers are saying...

           - I recently ordered a Regalia package from your company. Needless to say, I am VERY satisfied with your products. The sword far exceeded my expectations...it is beautifully done with outstanding craftsmanship. The cape, chapeau and chapeau carrying case along with the sword carrying case are all superbly made. Your customer service department was very kind, friendly and professional while working to make to sure I was satisfied with order. Your customer service is second to none!! Be assured I will ALWAYS give you a big 👍🏻👍🏻 up recommendation. Well done English Company!! Sincerely and fraternally, John S. 

           - I want to express my sincere thanks for your wonderful and expedient service  (wow!) Such professional and friendly service. We were surprised to get the order so fast.  From Marvin D. 

           - Just wanted to say "Thank You" again for the beautiful plaques for the  Council, they are perfect and look great! I appreciate all the help you have given to our brother knights! From Bill S. 

           - As F.N. of our Assembly, it is with great pride and pleasure that we extend to you and your staff, our gratitude for your prompt service to our requests for equipment. We have found that it only takes one phone call and your response time is outstanding and the supplies are excellent! Fraternally, Nestor D. 

           - As Master I bought all my gear through them great company and great people that work there. You buy from them and you get quality. Thank, Eugene D. 

